In https://github.com/ojkelly/yarn.build/pull/232 glob support was added to input/output.

Try the following in `package.json` of the package.

```
  "yarn.build": {
    "input": [
      "src/**",
      "!src/**/*.css"
    ],
    "output": [
      "src/**/*.css"
    ]
  },
```

